WEBVTT

00:12:28.117 --> 00:12:31.144
will be that this may be true,

00:12:31.168 --> 00:12:37.998
but there is still deeply offensive
sexism, racism, etc,

00:12:38.022 --> 00:12:42.363
and you can sound complacent in saying it.

00:12:42.387 --> 00:12:45.975
You're saying that we don't have to worry
about this anymore, Steve? Really?

00:12:45.999 --> 00:12:47.150
SP: No.

00:12:47.174 --> 00:12:49.993
What I always have to remind people

00:12:50.017 --> 00:12:53.903
is that there's a difference between
progress and perfection,

00:12:53.927 --> 00:12:57.129
that the fact that things are better now
than they were in the past,

00:12:57.153 --> 00:12:59.057
doesn't mean they're acceptable now.

00:12:59.081 --> 00:13:02.859
And in fact, quite the contrary
to complacency,